      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary mt-4 mb-8">
        Exploring the future of peer-to-peer economies, distributed systems, and
        new economic paradigms. Join me on this journey of understanding and
        building the next generation of economic systems.
      </p>

      <section class="my-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-main mb-8">
          What You'll Find Here
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div
            class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-dark/30 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-custom dark:shadow-custom-dark"
          >
