              ðŸ“š Content Types
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
              <li>In-depth Articles</li>
              <li>Technical Tutorials</li>
              <li>Case Studies</li>
              <li>Series & Guides</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-dark/30 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-custom dark:shadow-custom-dark"
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-main mb-4">
              ðŸŒŸ Special Features
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
